name: Does not enough space
description: What would Aristotle be like today? The Greek profile with a spiral flowing out of the ear, that's right, the brain is crawling out from the lack of space inside. It is a story with a deep message, a plot, and it is also a story of a tragic event that would take place today. A final chapter in the Aeneid. The story ends and the life takes its departure. However it would not be well if it were a tale of death and a melancholy. On the other hand the tale does not end in that way. We still carry me
